{"word":"H7231 - רָבַב - râbab - raw-bab' - Increase","slug":"H7231","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">רָבַב</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>râbab"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>raw-bab'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Increase"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E8;&#x05D1;&#x05D1; - ra&#x0302;bab</b> - <i>raw-bab'</i><p/>A primitive root; properly to <i>cast</i> together (compare <a href=\"#/H7241\">H7241</a>), that is, <i>increase</i>, especially in number; also (as denominative from <a href=\"#/H7233\">H7233</a>) to <i>multiply by the myriad: - </i>increase, be many (-ifold), be more, multiply, ten thousands."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3379\">H3379</a>, <a href=\"#/H7227\">H7227</a>, <a href=\"#/H7230\">H7230</a>, <a href=\"#/H7233\">H7233</a>, <a href=\"#/H7237\">H7237</a>, <a href=\"#/H7239\">H7239</a>, <a href=\"#/H7241\">H7241</a>, <a href=\"#/H7245\">H7245</a>, <a href=\"#/H7249\">H7249</a>, <a href=\"#/H7262\">H7262</a>"}]}